Uses of Package
bDIModel

  • Classes in bDIModel used by bDIModel 
    Class and Description
    Agent
    The Agent class objects have a ArrayList of Belief, Plan, Goal, Event and Import of the Agent.
    Belief
    The Belief class instantiates each Belief with initDate, validatedDate and Goal associated with the Belief.
    Event
    The Event class instantiates an Event with name and code.
    Goal
    The Goal class instantiates Goal with name, condition, goalType and the Goalplan associated with it.
    Import
    The Import class will handle the imports of the Agent.
    Plan
    The Plan class instantiates a Plan with name, code, PriorityValue and the planEvent associated with the Plan.
    XMLmodel
    The XMLmodel will handle the parsing of the XML input model.
